---
import CareerTimeline from "./CareerTimeline.astro";
import PullQuote from "./PullQuote.astro";
import SectionCTA from "./SectionCTA.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="px-6 lg:px-12 py-24 lg:py-32 max-w-[1280px] mx-auto scroll-mt-24">
  <header class="mb-16">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-6">Pillar · 01 / About</p>
    <p class="serif italic text-[20px] lg:text-[22px] text-paper-dim max-w-[680px] leading-[1.5]">
      Three careers. One throughline: figuring out the system before everyone else does.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="hairline pt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-16">
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-2">
      <h3 class="serif text-[clamp(34px,4.5vw,56px)] leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.01em] mb-12">
        Detective, then nurse, now <span class="accent">creator</span>. Same job, different tools.
      </h3>

      <p class="serif text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] leading-[1.7] text-paper/95 mb-6">
        <span class="float-left serif text-[88px] leading-[0.85] mr-3 mt-2 text-amber">I</span>
        spent two decades reading rooms, writing reports, and chasing facts in Baltimore. Then I traded a badge for scrubs and learned how a body falls apart, and how people put it back together at 3 a.m. on a med-surg floor.
      </p>

      <p class="serif text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] leading-[1.7] text-paper/95 mb-6">
        Now I make things. Music. Books. Photographs. Short films. I use AI like a detective uses a wiretap. One tool inside a process I actually understand.
      </p>

      <p class="serif text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] leading-[1.7] text-paper/95">
        Working with people who want the output, not the excuse. Remote-first. Based in Tampa, available worldwide.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-3 lg:col-start-10 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-paper-faint space-y-2">
      <p>Byline</p>
      <p class="serif italic text-amber text-[18px] normal-case tracking-normal">Keith Staggers</p>
      <p>Tampa, FL · Vol. III</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-24">
    <CareerTimeline />
  </div>

  <div class="mt-24">
    <PullQuote
      text='AI didn&rsquo;t make me a creator. Twenty years of chasing the truth & fixing broken bodies did. The tools just stopped getting in the way.'
      attribution="Manifesto"
    />
  </div>

  <SectionCTA prompt="Sound like a fit? Let's talk." />
</section>
